name: 'Hemisphere Series' girl's T
description:
In a more cerebral world right or left refers to personality traits, not beliefs. 
The ‘Hemisphere Series’, Unartisan’s latest collection of original apparel, 
explores the psyche through a collection of 24, 
one-of-a-kind, silk-screened t-shirts, 
each piece as original as the minds of those who wear them.

	Unartisan. Not just a garment. A statement.
